{"about_the_game":"In Crystals, you play as a kid who accidentally traveled to another Dimension, which is being terrorized by a ruthless Dimensional Warrior. It's up to our protagonist to defeat Dimensio and restore peace in the Dimension, so that he can return back home.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779180/extras/Protagonist_getting_thrown.gif?t=1710622871\" /><br><br>In Crystals, you can:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore areas based on elements such as fire, water, earth, electricity (bet you didn't expect this one) and sky<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779180/extras/Protagonist_walking.gif?t=1710622871\" /><br></li><li>Fight original enemies and avoid their attacks with a platformer-based system (don't worry you don't actually kill the enemies)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779180/extras/Battle_L._Volcano___F._Turtle.gif?t=1710622871\" /><br></li><li>Unlock abilities throughout the game by collecting crystals</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779180/extras/Crystal_of_Fire_activation.gif?t=1710622871\" /><br><br>Encounter special characters, fight against challenging enemies and intimidating bosses, live a story that you'll enjoy (how could you not like a game about a kid who barely knows basic math going to fight a bloody warrior who's able to tear apart a whole Dimension?)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779180/extras/H3LP_explaining.gif?t=1710622871\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779180/extras/Battle_John_Peestol.gif?t=1710622871\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779